<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:200px;"><img src="http://zok6hoi2.wdfiles.com/local--files/home%3Ahome/SCP_Jochoi_600px.png" style="width:200px;" alt="SCP_Jochoi_600px.png" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:200px;">
